title: Wake Up!
info:
A chiptune made on ATARI 520ST (YM chip).
Soft: MusicMon.

***Recorded from real hardware.***

After 17 years of having ATARI ST, this actually is my very first chiptune
for the machine. :)

Thx to Ato and all guyz from 
atari-forum.com

The song took the 2nd place in the SillyVenture 2012 ATARI party, on Atari ST/E chiptune music compo.
